               Transported for Fourteen Years
            </rs>. <rs id="t18170917-277-verdict1421" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18170917-277-verdict1421" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 27.</p>
               <p>Third Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
